## RscEntry.used property

Whether this entry is used in the DMB file

**Signature:**

```typescript
used: boolean;
```

## Remarks

When compiling a DMB file, unless the RSC file is deleted or a clean compile is request, entries that were previously included in the RSC file are not deleted. This field indicates whether this entry is in use or not.
